            <title>[SOLR-202] parseQueryString should use UTF-8</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-202</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;update handler should explicitly use UTF-8 decoding  for parameters in the query string:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   URLDecoder.decode( kv, &quot;UTF-8&quot; );&lt;/p&gt;</description>
